About this item

  • Powerful PerformanceGaming laptop with built-in 12th Gen Alder Lake N95 processor with speeds up to 3.4GHz and 6MB Cache, this Witraditional laptop computers delivers powerful all-around performance for efficient creativity and daily productivity. Moreover, equipped with 16 GB DDR4 and 1T SSD, providing more powerful multitasking capabilities.
  • Amazing 16-inch FHD DisplayLaptop computer boasts a brand new 16-inch 2560*1600, 240Hz display with stunning detail and ultra-vivid colors, a page-friendly 16:10 aspect ratio, and a 92% screen-to-body ratio that gives you stunning visuals whether you're working, studying, watching movies, or entertaining. In addition, the work laptop can be folded 180, you can adjust the comfortable Angle at any time.
  • High Speed & Enormous SpaceWith built-in 16GB RAM and 1T SSD, the work laptop can effortlessly manage multiple programs simultaneously, greatly improving system responsiveness and storage speed, enabling efficient and smooth multitasking and high-volume data access for all your data needs. Moreover, the thin laptop has a 5000mAh battery built in, and the smart cooling system runs in the background to keep it cold under high loads and minimize cooling noise.
  • Webcam & Fingerprint ReaderBusiness laptop with fingerprint reader has a built-in 720p HD physical webcam privacy shield, time noise reduction, and an integrated dual-array digital microphone. At the same time, the built-in fingerprint reader strengthens the protection of personal privacy and information security. In addition, the full-size backlit keyboard enhances the convenience of laptop typing. The independent numeric keyboard makes input faster and more convenient. At the same time, press Fn F5 to open the backlit keyboard.
  • Peace of Mind WarrantyTuonoyee's customer service team will be there for you, and our laptop computer comes with a one-year warranty and lifetime technical support. If you have any questions, please get in touch with us via Amazon and our customer service.

    How customer reviews and ratings work

    Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

    To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
